            "answer_text": "Yes!They are critical of everyone and everything - partly because they think they are better than everyone and everything and partly because they are envious of everyone and everything. They are two-faced in public to hide their criticisms but in private, YOU get the brunt of the criticism (and then get accused of not being able to handle criticism!)Narcs are hypocritical too. Their own rules don't apply to them.Being with a narc messes with your mind because their own minds are messed up. If my narc ever criticised himself, it was VERY short-lived before someone was getting the blame instead. ",
